## Tech Stack

### Frontend  
- Frameworks & Libraries: Next.js 14, React 18, shadcn/ui, react-query, Apollo Client  
- Styling: TailwindCSS, Slate.js, react-perfect-scrollbar  

### Backend  
- Server & API: Express.js, GraphQL  

### Database  
- Databases: MongoDB, IndexedDB (via RxDB)  
- State Management & Sync: RxDB, rxdb-hooks, Web Workers  

### Tooling & Build  
- Build & Bundling: Vite, tsup, TurboRepo  
- Configuration: ESLint, Tailwind config, TSConfig  

### Testing  
- Testing Framework: Vitest  

### CI/CD & Package Management  
- Versioning & Releasing: GitLab CI/CD, GitLab Package Registry, monorepo setup  

### Other  
- React Utilities Library: TypeScript-based  
- GraphQL Tooling: GraphQL Codegen